{"itemid":1764,"subject":"Three Cheers For Snod","event":"Wanted to take a moment here to congratulate my old friend, sometimes collarborator, co-editor, and general partner in crime MELINDA M. SNODGRASS on her new gig.  Melinda is headed back to LA to head up the writing staff of STAR TREK: RENEGADES, a new fan-funded Trek web series that features Walter Koenig as Chekov.  Melinda will be an executive producer.\r\n\r\nOf course, Snod is no stranger to Trek.  She was one of the writers on NEXT GENERATION, where she scripted, among other episodes, \"Measure of a Man,\" still widely regarded as one of the best five Trek episodes of all team.  She'll do a great job on this new show, I have no doubt.\r\n\r\nYou can read all about this on Melinda's own blog at:\r\n              http://melindasnodgrass.com/star-trek-renegades\r\n\r\n((I know a lot of you Trek fans out there will be excited about this, and there will doubtless be lots of questions... that's the place to ask 'em, not here.  Thanks.))\r\n\r\nAlso, here's the link to the Kickstarter page funding RENEGADES:\r\n     https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/145553614/star-trek-renegades-episodes-2-and-3   \r\n\r\nSounds like a fun series.  Go get 'em, Weeds.","ditemid":451592,"eventtime":"2015-10-29 14:30:00","props":{"current_location":"Santa Fe","taglist":"friends, television","commentalter":1446421782,"homepage_reposted":63986505,"crosspost_tw":"Three Cheers For Snod http://goo.gl/CP4sV5","opt_lockcomments":1,"picture_keyword":"thumbs up","opt_screening":"F","personifi_tags":"nterms:yes","interface":"web","revnum":1,"langs":"{\"languages\":[[\"eng\",0.617759366744899]],\"detector\":\"Lingua-YALI:0.015\",\"updated\":1446150639}","revtime":1447096572},"can_comment":0,"logtime":"2015-10-29 20:30:05","anum":8,"url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/451592.html","event_timestamp":1446129000,"reply_count":10,"comments":[{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/125221567/76479096","actions":[{"all